subSubSection.paragraph:
Movements, Home range and Social organization.
Holotype of Marinkelle’s Swordnosed Bat was sharing a roost with two Orinoco Sword-nosed Bats (
Lonchorhina orinocensis
), Seba’s Short-tailed Bats (
Carollia perspicillata
), Orange-throated Bats (
Lampronycteris brachyotis
), and Lesser Dog-like Bats (
Peropteryx macrotis
).
